      <title>美国情报部门指责伊朗对特朗普竞选活动进行黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/us-intelligence-points-finger-at-iran-in-trump-campaign-hack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构表示，他们“确信”伊朗是最近针对前总统唐纳德·特朗普总统竞选活动黑客攻击的幕后黑手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/us-intelligence-points-finger-at-iran-in-trump-campaign-hack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多伦多、蒙特利尔、温哥华通勤者因铁路罢工而受到影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/toronto-montreal-vancouver-commuters-face-disruption-from-rail-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从周四开始，加拿大最大城市的工人通勤可能会更加困难，因为如果公司和工会不能达成协议，该国最大的两条铁路将会关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/toronto-montreal-vancouver-commuters-face-disruption-from-rail-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为美联储批评辩护，考虑向购房者提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/trump-defends-fed-criticism-weighs-providing-aid-to-home-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普淡化了对他削弱美联储自主权的批评，称他应该能够自由地分享他对利率政策的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/trump-defends-fed-criticism-weighs-providing-aid-to-home-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:46:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和夏皮罗打击销售乐观情绪，美国钢铁股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/us-steel-shares-fall-as-trump-shapiro-deflate-sale-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前总统特朗普和宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗再次表示反对新日本制铁公司收购美国钢铁公司，后者股价出现5个月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/us-steel-shares-fall-as-trump-shapiro-deflate-sale-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 20:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在传递火炬之际最后一次登台回顾</title>
